{"tid":1426811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急!!] call馬護新聞女神—利君雅","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:17:13.000Z","uid":269096,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e08b2251dbe0bc6f568b554ce575a9377fbc872d","tid":1426811,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"聽聞港台最近收到好多關於利君雅既投訴<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手支援真港人利君雅!<br />\n<br />\nccu@rthk.hk; <br />\n<br />\nchanmw@rthk.hk; <br />\n<br />\narchives@rthk.hk; <br />\n<br />\ndtt@rthk.hk; webmaster@rthk.hk; <br />\n<br />\nradio1@rthk.hk; radio2@rthk.hk; radio3@rthk.hk; radio4@rthk.hk; radio5@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n可以copy and paste 或者share 比friend. <br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n致香港電台：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本人為香港電台的長期觀眾。我想對利君雅記者作出簡單而直接的感謝。<br />\n<br />\n利君雅記者在香港動盪的時候，發揮出色的記者工作。對官員的問題一針見血，對政府種種迴避的態度加以追問。對社會現狀有獨到見解，以理性及中立的態度去揭示香港種種問題。<br />\n<br />\n請香港電台，代本人向利君雅記者轉達謝意。亦希望香港電台可以繼續保持中立，以事實報道真相。<br />\n<br />\nDear RTHK, <br />\n<br />\nI am a RTHK regular audience for many years. I would like to express my sincerest gratitude to journalist Ms. Nabela Qoser. She has shown bravery and the spirit of being a journalist, seeking the truth during this difficult time in Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nI am no expert in journalism but Ms. Nabela Qoser have raised questions in the recent press conferences that many of us have wanted to ask. She has revealed the truth that I needed to see with facts and evidence. <br />\n<br />\nPlease pass on my greatest appreciation to Ms. Nabela Qoser&rsquo;s outstanding work and dedication. We need more reporters like her.<br />\n<br />\nxxx<br />\n<br />\nXxxxx2019"},{"pid":"7d2773a1ecf3e9a31d104a3ffb767ad6ac76ab68","tid":1426811,"uid":269096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"食lunch 都係睇手機架啦，不如就send個email 先聲援利君雅"},{"pid":"3cd685a52c535af177f823d9a36bdb6e6fbf123f","t